  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to CENTRAL INTELLIGENCE EXPERIMENTAL BRANCH. </strong> <br><br>A new world needs to be explored and our world does not know you exist.  Your perfect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/5a73f831e32b3665336e529135a9b1b8.poster.avif?t=1727672015\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/5a73f831e32b3665336e529135a9b1b8.webm?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/5a73f831e32b3665336e529135a9b1b8.mp4?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We were in control of a very teensy tiny bit of the backrooms. Our information and data were left behind during the Flicker. We need you to bring it back to us.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/b11a1c4bd7e94c05843d0dfae9d2660c.poster.avif?t=1727672015\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/b11a1c4bd7e94c05843d0dfae9d2660c.webm?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/b11a1c4bd7e94c05843d0dfae9d2660c.mp4?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want something to buy then research it. Once we can replicate it, we will sell it back to you.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/65938e9ca671e50c6751ce60690c5fb6.poster.avif?t=1727672015\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/65938e9ca671e50c6751ce60690c5fb6.webm?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/65938e9ca671e50c6751ce60690c5fb6.mp4?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not falter if things dont make sense. Very little is known of this world but disorder and fear.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to CENTRAL INTELLIGENCE EXPERIMENTAL BRANCH. </strong> <br><br>A new world needs to be explored and our world does not know you exist.  Your perfect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/5a73f831e32b3665336e529135a9b1b8.poster.avif?t=1727672015\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/5a73f831e32b3665336e529135a9b1b8.webm?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/5a73f831e32b3665336e529135a9b1b8.mp4?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We were in control of a very teensy tiny bit of the backrooms. Our information and data were left behind during the Flicker. We need you to bring it back to us.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/b11a1c4bd7e94c05843d0dfae9d2660c.poster.avif?t=1727672015\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/b11a1c4bd7e94c05843d0dfae9d2660c.webm?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/b11a1c4bd7e94c05843d0dfae9d2660c.mp4?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want something to buy then research it. Once we can replicate it, we will sell it back to you.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/65938e9ca671e50c6751ce60690c5fb6.poster.avif?t=1727672015\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/65938e9ca671e50c6751ce60690c5fb6.webm?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259360/extras/65938e9ca671e50c6751ce60690c5fb6.mp4?t=1727672015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not falter if things dont make sense. Very little is known of this world but disorder and fear.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
